</span></span></code></pre></div><p>接下来继续在 <code>custom.scss</code> 添加以下内容：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-scss" data-lang="scss"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">//----------------------------------------------------------
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">//为代码块顶部添加macos样式
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"></span><span style="color:#a6e22e">.article-content</span> {
