</span></span></code></pre></div><p>接下来在 <code>custom.scss</code> 中添加如下：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-scss" data-lang="scss"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">//首页欢迎板块样式
